{"tid":1915874,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Facebook 宣布禁止用戶賣有關醫療用口罩的廣告或刊登相關銷售內容","createTime":"2020-03-08T13:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T14:59:54.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a4a2915440bfb08ed3fcdb5a96a2a11ad8b57096","tid":1915874,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T13:45:59.000Z","msg":"「兩盒, thx!」是不少 Facebook 預訂口罩貼文常見的回覆，不過這個情況稍後可能會有所改變。Facebook 的產品管理總監 Rob Leathern 在 Twitter 表示，在未來數日將會有新的措施，今次用戶在 Facebook 賣有關醫療用口罩的廣告或刊登相關銷售內容。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2580000/2584352/0308_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2580000%2F2584352%2F0308_1024.png&h=f761bc4d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nFacebook 早在 1 月就已經禁止刊登宣稱醫療物品為限量供應，或能殺滅和預防新冠狀病毒的產品廣告，同時又將以武漢肺炎作主題的群組和專頁，從他們的演算法中剔除，Facebook 將措施進一步延伸至醫療用口罩產品，是為了避免賣家透過疫情發國難財。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/03/08/facebook-instagram-bans-ads-face-masks-coronavirus/life-tech/health/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F03%2F08%2Ffacebook-instagram-bans-ads-face-masks-coronavirus%2Flife-tech%2Fhealth%2F&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5BwzDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=73d9341a\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/03/08/facebook-instagram-bans-ads-face-masks-coronavirus/life-tech/health/</a>"},{"pid":"4eef91a7dc49c560ae7f065734ba489f680759d2","tid":1915874,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T13:46:07.000Z","msg":"同時間，Instagram 亦會配合母公司 Facebook，推出相同措施。Instagram 負責人 Adam Mosseri 表示供應短缺，售價上升，他們反對人們藉公共衛生緊急狀況牟取暴利。"},{"pid":"05b77568a08f33e67a5a1d89597f2786bdd06fab","tid":1915874,"uid":139322,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T13:49:45.000Z","msg":"定幫中共減少武肺討論"},{"pid":"8e9124b458966fe00c5a7f67447ea3e0e3692bf4","tid":1915874,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T13:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bq70aOE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBq70aOE.jpg&h=84a3d903&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41cd96417e25fe3b75691b2b049032bfa699bf23","tid":1915874,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T14:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}